  <brief_title>Vaginal Cuff Dehiscence at Total Laparoscopic Hysterectomy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Vaginal Cuff Dehiscence After Two Different Colpotomy Techniques at Total Laparoscopic Hysterectomy; a Randomized Clinical Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
